Simple tool to get poll info from http://news.ycombinator.com

INSTRUCTIONS

To setup the environment :

pip install -r requirements.txt

To run the test cases :

python test_case.py

To use the tool on cli :

python lib/poll.py http://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=3146321

To generate html from hackernews polls(default is last 10):

python test_web.py

To get last 2 polls :

python test_web.py 2

After that check the file poll.html for results(Now supports visual charts).

